  "response_text": "The commercial opens in a bright, modern office-like space with white walls, fluorescent ceiling panels, desks, and people working in the background. Three young adult women sit close together on a white bench or low platform, facing forward. The woman in the center is the focus: she has a straight, light-brown bob haircut with bangs and wears a long-sleeved, multicolored plaid dress with a bow at the neck and a belt. She smiles directly ahead. On her left sits a brunette woman in a pale lavender blouse and a rose-pink skirt; on her right sits a blonde woman in a vivid blue dress with a dark belt. Both side women look toward the center woman and then toward the viewer, smiling and attentive.\n\nThe center woman lifts a tall red-and-white package from her lap and holds it upright in front of her chest. The package shows the “Today’s Girl” name and a picture of a seated woman’s legs, presenting it as pantyhose packaging. The women remain seated with their knees and lower legs visible, their sheer hosiery emphasized by the way they sit and angle their legs. The center woman gestures down toward her own leg while keeping the package visible, then all three settle into a wider seated pose on the white platform, their legs extended or crossed in a way that displays the pantyhose.\n\nThe center woman rises from the bench while still holding the package. She steps forward, smiling, with the brunette and blonde remaining seated behind her for a moment. As she stands in front of them, the two women behind extend their legs outward from the bench, one on each side, as if comparing the look of their hosiery with hers. The office setting becomes clearer behind them: desks, papers, seated workers, and a few standing people create a busy but tidy workplace background.\n\nThe center woman begins walking forward through the office, holding the Today’s Girl package against her side. The brunette in the pink skirt and the blonde in the blue dress stand and follow behind her. As they move, the brunette briefly lifts one leg out to the side, showing the sheer pantyhose on her leg. The center woman continues smiling and talking toward the viewer while the other two trail slightly behind, glancing at each other and at their legs.\n\nThe center woman moves to the right foreground and sits again on the edge of a white surface, still holding the red-and-white package. Her legs are visible in front of her, and she angles the package so its front label can be seen. Behind her, the brunette and blonde stand facing each other in the office area, looking down and gesturing toward their own skirts and legs as if responding to the comparison. The brunette lifts her knee and leg again in a small demonstration, while the blonde stands beside her in the blue dress, smiling. White on-screen text near the bottom reads “SUGGESTED RETAIL PRICE” during this portion.\n\nThe center woman remains seated in the right foreground, smiling broadly with the product package resting in her hands. She raises one hand beside her face in an open, upbeat gesture while the other two women stand to the left, watching and reacting. The office background stays active but secondary, with desks, coworkers, and a vase of white flowers visible nearby.\n\nThe commercial ends on a black background with a product display. On the left is the red Today’s Girl pantyhose package, showing the brand name “today’s girl” and a photo of a woman seated with her legs visible. Near the top center is a small portrait of the center woman from the commercial. Large white text reads, “Choose it for the quality. Buy it for the price.” Beneath it, the price “$1.19” is shown.",
